<F P=100> Military </F>
<H3> <TI>   Jinan Military Region Holds Spring Festival Party </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK1102062494 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 10 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK1102062494 </F>
<F P=104>  Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] On the morning of 10 February, more than 2,000 
people of the military region gathered happily at Bayi 
Auditorium to attend the Spring Festival gathering and 
celebrations for organs of the military region. 
  Leading comrades of the military region and of organs of the 
military region, including Zhang Taiheng, Song Qingwei, and 
veteran leaders of the military region, zealously celebrated the 
Spring Festival and spent the festive day along with the people. 
  Political Commissar Song Qingwei presided over this 
gathering 
and Commander Zhang Taiheng addressed it. First of all, he 
wished a happy Spring Festival to veteran leaders of the 
military region, and to all cadres, soldiers, workers, and staff 
families of organs and subordinate units of the military region, 
and extended festive greetings and cordial regards to comrades 
on behalf of the standing committee of the party committee of 
the military region. 
  He said: The past year was one during which the officers and 
men at the higher and the lower level throughout the military 
region worked with one heart and one mind, exerted vigorous 
efforts to forge ahead, and won greater progress in 
comprehensively building the Army. The whole Army was full of 
vigor and vitality. We should attributed all this to the 
regular hard work of the officers and men throughout the 
military region. This year, the work tasks of Army building 
will be heavier and more arduous. We should strive to meet the 
demands of the new situation, actively strengthen the 
self-development of various organs, realistically turn them into 
a group of leading organs with a strong political sense, good 
professional skills, solid work style, and high working 
efficiency, lead the Army units across the military region to 
comprehensively implement Chairman Jiang's proposal of building 
the Army into a politically qualified Army with a perfect 
mastery of military skills, strict discipline, and good work 
style that can defend the country effectively, and successfully 
fulfill all tasks entrusted by the higher level. 
  Commander Zhang Taiheng called on commanders and fighters 
across the military region to work with one heart and one mind, 
engage in arduous struggle, actively seek new development in 
Army building, and strive to create a new situation in building 
the Army under the correct leadership of the party Central 
Committee with Comrade Jiang 
  Zemin as the nucleus and the Central Military Commission. 
  Colorful large-scale Spring Festival celebrations were held 
after the gathering. 

</TEXT>

