Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, February 17 (XINHUA) -- Giovanni Spatolini, 
president of the Senate of Italy will pay a goodwill visit to 
China from February 18 to 23 at the invitation of the Standing 
Committee of China's National People's Congress. This was 
announced by a spokesman of the Chinese Foreign Ministry at a 
